Class LabelBasedAbstraction

Direct Known Subclasses:
ReachableFromAbstraction, ReachableFromAllocAbstraction, ReachableFromAllocPlusFieldsAbstraction
public abstract class LabelBasedAbstraction
extends Abstraction

The abstraction of concrete node o is a set of LabelBasedAbstraction.Labels. LabelBasedAbstraction enforces and maintains the following invariant: If o2 is reachable from o1, then the set of labels associated with o2 is a superset of the set of labels associated with o1. An invariant resulting from the above invariant is that the set of labels associated with node o is the union of the sets of labels associated with o's parents, plus the labels rooted at o.

Author:
omertripp (omertrip@post.tau.ac.il)
